 223:.\Source\rte/sc_event.h **** /**
 224:.\Source\rte/sc_event.h ****  * Returns the count of refreshing trials (refresh, set or set_raw) that failed.
 225:.\Source\rte/sc_event.h ****  * Prerquisite: The signal is refreshed cyclically
 226:.\Source\rte/sc_event.h ****  *
 227:.\Source\rte/sc_event.h ****  * @param  SC_EVENT_t * const signal: Pointer to the signal object
